Class Resume

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.hr.data.Resume
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Resume
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Resume>
    Class that holds the resume information. The resume information consists of resume ID, the number of service years served and the highest degree earned.

    Jimmy Nguyen
